{"tid":714282,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到底毒撚邊到先可以識到朋友啊！好想搵人傾計啊！","createTime":"2018-06-23T14:40:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T01:24:12.000Z","uid":43327,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"0225e7df8cbfc5e9736a654e9be5d3673248d0c2","tid":714282,"uid":43327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:40:33.000Z","msg":"我只係一個識返工收工既死毒撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nd人話報興趣班，但我由細到大真係乜興趣專長都無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd人話 join telegram whatsapp group，但我次次都 topic killer <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解我會搞成咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8074a132a90b12496630b1e702a1c0a09b6e1c","tid":714282,"uid":138138,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"真毒係唔會嘗試改變，例如我"},{"pid":"c7806272bcfa8674ff07af90f087c2f9a2d1560d","tid":714282,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:43:11.000Z","msg":"毒撚去到邊都冇人想同佢做朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e03cc4bd7706dacd7d823112cdc6ed30cc46d6","tid":714282,"uid":14214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d8074a132a90b12496630b1e702a1c0a09b6e1c","tid":714282,"uid":138138,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"真毒係唔會嘗試改變，例如我"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:44:01.000Z","msg":"頂 講緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3e933306880f7ffcf46ec6b93d31e39a336077","tid":714282,"uid":43327,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"問題係，我唔知點解返工比人印象係 talkative <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返工 9up 下人地都會彩下我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但收工之後你真係甚麼也不是 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61adce028e079408e92060227c2650e93e5b7432","tid":714282,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0e03cc4bd7706dacd7d823112cdc6ed30cc46d6","tid":714282,"uid":14214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d8074a132a90b12496630b1e702a1c0a09b6e1c","tid":714282,"uid":138138,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"真毒係唔會嘗試改變，例如我"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:44:01.000Z","msg":"頂 講緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:47:20.000Z","msg":"係咪a0 先，唔係既你可以出番去"},{"pid":"bc0f3d1584c2cffda266dde4da76799321d591bb","tid":714282,"uid":112161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:49:59.000Z","msg":"唔好諗識唔識到朋友先<br />\n無自己嘅興趣做咩都無用"},{"pid":"d47b477c025fa51e5b77c6dd9c3615eb2f2aa353","tid":714282,"uid":43327,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:50:42.000Z","msg":"毒撚努力工作，三年，五年，七年過去了，依然沒有朋友。毒撚成為高收入人仕 － 月薪達二萬零五百蚊。<br />\n<br />\n毒撚年過三十，開始疑惑：「點解我已經係成功人仕，但仲係無朋友？」更令他驚訝的是，公司不少同事都很多朋友，但那些人都是一事無成喎，例如，Dorothy既只係中五畢業既Sales，月薪只有一萬八千蚊，比自己足足少了二千多元！點解？高登仔唔係話努力讀書成為有錢人就有朋友既咩？<br />\n<br />\n不知不覺毒撚到了中年，身邊已無什麼朋友，自己渡過一個又一個既聖誕節及情人節。<br />\n<br />\n毒撚年老了，孤零零一個坐在公園，回想一生：「自己曾得過什麼？同朋友傾計是怎麼樣的？和朋友係吹天光 9up 既滋味係點架？高登仔不是經常留帖話：『後生時唔好浪費時間，第時有錢你荒無朋友咩！』我照做了，究竟什麼地方出錯？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/225040_f05696d68efebea62c755c3056533ba1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F225040_f05696d68efebea62c755c3056533ba1.jpeg&h=8e7374f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7964e5496f265f59d84824487d0bd642b463199","tid":714282,"uid":180572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒撚係識唔到朋友"},{"pid":"572dcbc0871290a84d97b953857981db4dafbc03","tid":7